~ 0 NEWBIE~
#g--------------------------------------------------------------------------------#n
#n Innocence Lost RPI#y -#n HELP DATABASE
#g--------------------------------------------------------------------------------#n
Welcome to Innocence Lost, a Chronicles of Darkness RPI-lite!

The first thing you should be aware of is the #wADVICE#n channel. Trolling or funny
answers are not permitted over #wADVICE#n; you will always get a serious, legitimate
answer to your questions. To speak over #wADVICE#n, use: #gadvice How do I...?#n

All monitoring Staff may be contacted with the #wREQUEST#n command. To contact the
Staff, use: #grequest I'm stuck!#n

Our website and Wiki are located at #wlishmud.com#n and #wlishmud.com/wiki#n. We strive
to keep the in-game helpfiles up to date, but if you cannot locate something in
a helpfile, the Wiki is always a good next step.

We are not an application-based RPI. You do not need to wait for Staff to review
your character before entering play. Once you have progressed through in-game
character generation, you are able to enter the game and begin play.

Note that we do not have mobs to kill or automated quests. The sole purpose of
the game is roleplay. Combat is carried out with our d10 dice roller, and
descriptive #wposes#n #g(help pose)#n.

We are not a consent-based MUD, and death is permanent.

Please let Staff know if you need help, have an idea for improvement, or simply
want a little guidance. We are happy to help!
#g--------------------------------------------------------------------------------#n
 See Also: DEATH
