#g|#n and "on ground" (long) description. To set the descriptions for your        #g|#n
#g|#n vehicle's interior and exterior, use restring with "inside" and "outside."  #g|#n
#g|#n                                                                             #g|#n
#g|#e restring <vehicle keyword> #Ginside #e<Description string goes here. A few      #g|#n
